@startuml Error_Handling_Sensor_Failure
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center
skinparam responseMessageBelowArrow true
skinparam BoxPadding 10

title Error Handling - Sensor Failure Sequence

participant "STM32" as STM32
participant "SHT31" as SHT31
participant "DS3231" as DS3231
participant "ESP32" as ESP32
participant "MQTT Broker" as MQTT
participant "app.js" as AppJS
participant "Firebase" as Firebase
participant "Browser" as Browser

note over STM32: Periodic measurement triggered
activate STM32
STM32 -> SHT31: I2C read request
activate SHT31

alt Sensor Disconnected/Failed
    SHT31 --> STM32: No response / NACK
    deactivate SHT31

    STM32 -> STM32: Detect I2C error\nSet temp = 0.0, humi = 0.0

    STM32 -> DS3231: I2C read RTC (still works)
    activate DS3231
    DS3231 --> STM32: Valid timestamp
    deactivate DS3231

    STM32 -> STM32: Format JSON\n{"temperature":0.0,"humidity":0.0,"timestamp":X}

    STM32 -> ESP32: UART transmit error JSON
    deactivate STM32
    activate ESP32
    ESP32 -> MQTT: Publish(periodicData)
    deactivate ESP32
    activate MQTT
    MQTT -> AppJS: Forward message
    deactivate MQTT
    activate AppJS

    AppJS -> AppJS: Parse JSON
    AppJS -> AppJS: Check: temp == 0.0 && humi == 0.0

    AppJS -> AppJS: sensorFailed = true
    AppJS -> AppJS: addStatus("ERROR: SHT31 sensor hardware failed\n(disconnected or wiring issue)")
    AppJS -> AppJS: addStatus("WARNING: Sensor hardware failed")

    AppJS -> AppJS: updateComponentHealth(SHT31, false)
    AppJS -> AppJS: componentHealth.SHT31.healthy = false\nerrorCount++

    AppJS -> Browser: Update component card\n#component-SHT31
    activate Browser
    AppJS -> Browser: Badge: disconnected "Error"
    AppJS -> Browser: #sht31-temp = "Sensor Failed"\n#sht31-humi = "Check Wiring"\n#sht31-time = "Error"
    deactivate Browser

    AppJS -> AppJS: Save to Firebase\nstatus = "error"\nerror = "sensor_fail"

    AppJS -> Firebase: Save record with error flag
    activate Firebase
    Firebase --> AppJS: Write complete
    deactivate Firebase

    AppJS -> AppJS: Skip chart update\n(Don't push 0 values)

    AppJS -> AppJS: addToLiveDataTable\nstatus = "error"
    AppJS -> Browser: Render error row\nRed badge "✗ Error"
    activate Browser
    deactivate Browser

    AppJS -> Browser: Console shows error logs
    activate Browser
    deactivate Browser
    deactivate AppJS
end

@enduml